                        destination, picking suitable venues, consultation, planning, designing, and
                        coordination are all taken care of by our professional team.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <button class="accordion"><span>Is it expensive to hire a wedding planner?</span></button>
                <div class="panel">
                    <p>
