                        by virtue of our vast network of vendors that we strive on preferential rates passing on
                        to you to benefit from. Our prime focus is to deliver a memorable wedding celebration
                        for you keeping in view your budgets and expectations.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <button class="accordion">
                    <span>
                        Does The Planning Paradise provide services
                        overseas?
                    </span>
                </button>
                <div class="panel">
                    <p>
                        As we plan and manage exclusive destination weddings, our services can be affianced
                        globally. We have created up to 300+ enchanted weddings so far, each of them
                        marvellously unique and magical from the other working with a vast network of vendors
                        internationally in numerous cities around the world.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <button class="accordion">
                    <span>
                        What kind of weddings does The Planning Paradise specialize
                        in?
                    </span>
                </button>
                <div class="panel">
                    <p>
                        Although we specialize in Indian weddings, we have also planned and managed weddings of
                        different cultures and religions across different customs and traditions. Our
                        acquaintance and experience is not just limited to traditional weddings. Our team have
                        the potential and expertise to propose various ground-breaking concepts for your big
                        day.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <button class="accordion">
                    <span>
                        Can The Planning Paradise assist if we bring our own
                        vendors?
                    </span>
                </button>
                <div class="panel">
                    <p>
                        Apart from our vendor association, our clients have the ease and comfort of working with
