                </div>

                <button class="accordion">
                    <span>
                        What precautions is The Planning Paradise taking with the
                        present health and safety challenges?
                    </span>
                </button>
                <div class="panel">
                    <p>
                        The Planning Paradise have constantly preserved the uppermost canons of safety, health,
                        and hygiene. During the present times our team members ensure the services to be in
                        terms of Health & Safety, as well as trained for COVID-19 Precautions and Guidelines.
