                </div>

                <button class="accordion"><span>How does the Force Majeure protect me?</span></button>
                <div class="panel">
                    <p>
                        If any inevitable incident or an Act of God (Force Majeure), such as a fire, flood,
                        earthquake, pandemic, or other natural calamity that shall cause you to cancel your
                        event; we will we assist you with contract flexibility and refunds where eligible.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <button class="accordion">
                    <span>
                        Does your team take on the liaison with our guests and RSVP
                        Management?
                    </span>
                </button>
                <div class="panel">
                    <p>
                        Indians firmly believe that Guests are next to GOD and hence we would love knowing your
                        family and friends better. We highly cherish our principles and customs and make every
                        effort to provide comfort and a home like feeling to the guest arrived at your wedding.
