                    </p>
                </div>

                <button class="accordion">
                    <span>
                        Will Hardik & Darshita be planning and managing my
                        wedding?
                    </span>
                </button>
                <div class="panel">
                    <p>
                        Our Founder Director Hardik & Co-Founder Darshita trails the wedding planning and
                        management business virtuously out of their passion for creating memorable memories for
                        the bride and groom and their guests. Being resourceful Wedding Planners of
                        International standards, they are adept at planning and executing high-end weddings with
                        latest and up-to-date trends as well as conceptual themes of modern times
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<!-- FAQ's Accordion End -->
<script>
    var acc = document.getElementsByClassName("accordion");
    var i;

    for (i = 0; i < acc.length; i++) {
        acc[i].addEventListener("click", function () {
            this.classList.toggle("active");
            var panel = this.nextElementSibling;
            if (panel.style.maxHeight) {
                panel.style.maxHeight = null;
            } else {
                panel.style.maxHeight = panel.scrollHeight + "px";
            }
        });
    }
</script>